objects.name: Level_text_filler
objects.string:
Alright, here's the rundown:
WASD to move
Left click to shoot
Right Click to Dash
R to reload
Q to activate patches (power ups)
T to cycle patches
E to interact (doors, hatches, and shops)

Here's where it gets complex:
Every "patch" (power up) you pick up will not start off at in its strongest form, and needs to be uploaded in order to enter its best form. You can either wait out the timer or overclock ("f") to speed it up. Overclocking costs health though. Alright, that's it. Good luck (you're gonna need it)

Your objective: Survive
